{"tid":2027782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"決意離開波台, 這是我在這裡出的最後一個post","createTime":"2020-05-21T13:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T01:20:34.000Z","uid":79562,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"38c4297ac6e9f15aa8f298950cf05bd2e6462209","tid":2027782,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:44:00.000Z","msg":"這裏的人學識都很高<br />\n<br />\n從這裏的人的留言中學會了很多知識<br />\n<br />\n天文, 地理, 氣象, 歷史, 政治<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是我一上網就立刻到這裏的原因<br />\n<br />\n正正是因為我自己都是一個愛好知識的人<br />\n<br />\n加上這裏的人都多廿靚歲的, 同我相若, 岩傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我在這裡出了很多很多post, 但99%都是所謂的 &quot;假膠post&quot;, 即是完完全全亂up老作搏大家一笑,<br />\n<br />\n帖內的內容和自己的事完全沒關, 無論出post同reply都係, 甚至好多時同真實既自己係相反<br />\n<br />\n明明是利物浦球迷, 卻經常出post揶揄利物浦<br />\n<br />\n明明自己都係工程界人士, 卻經常出post話工程界一文不值<br />\n<br />\n明明自己極討厭某個死港女, 就出post話自己愛上左佢<br />\n<br />\n歸根究抵都係純粹因為工作時無聊, 所以無無聊聊地出個post<br />\n<br />\n講無聊野<br />\n<br />\n然後一邊工作, 一邊睇回覆, 自娛一下<br />\n<br />\n這件事對不喜歡現在的工作的我十分重要<br />\n<br />\n同時, 我故意講相反野, 因為驚俾人知我既真正身份<br />\n<br />\n一個知...就會話俾另一個知, 然後一傳十, 十傳百, 就不好了, 我完全唔想俾人知我o係網上既身份, 講過 d 乜<br />\n<br />\n俾人知道, 我o係呢度暢所欲言, 說傻話, 減減壓的空間就完全被破壞了...<br />\n(雖然我出既post都同自己做過既野無關)<br />\n<br />\n不過, 有一日我忽然發現自己沉迷了這裡....荒廢正業<br />\n<br />\n離開, 因為不想再在這裏浪費時間了, 往後我還有很多計劃, 操番好體能, 籌備上雪山, 練番水, 練好 d 壁球, 鋼琴要考演奏級, 練好渣車, 重投放下了一年多的義工活動, 抽多 d 時間陪女朋友, 考番CFA (讀好左level 1 又因病冇考)...etc etc<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再見了, 波台各位高學識既人."},{"pid":"204c43a365a933a6e1a48d5d7dd31468dacc54ac","tid":2027782,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"Gun"},{"pid":"914e379de9e27358708c3feea11d0b0033d82c37","tid":2027782,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"204c43a365a933a6e1a48d5d7dd31468dacc54ac","tid":2027782,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"Gun"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:48:55.000Z","msg":"明叔<br />\n無得反你反利了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50164f7b7d96500e59e563a91739cdefd55f36f8","tid":2027782,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c284914af07f3afa4c7b1154a8f06138868d2b6","tid":2027782,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"914e379de9e27358708c3feea11d0b0033d82c37","tid":2027782,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"204c43a365a933a6e1a48d5d7dd31468dacc54ac","tid":2027782,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"Gun"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:48:55.000Z","msg":"明叔<br />\n無得反你反利了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:50:01.000Z","msg":"反我嘅人注定收皮"},{"pid":"9b6ad6fd143cbe6f58e3a8ebd7408bacd4772989","tid":2027782,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50164f7b7d96500e59e563a91739cdefd55f36f8","tid":2027782,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2b5d6e8953768422ef84e5728e3c3c35ac699e","tid":2027782,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"挽留高質會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e83b35fe49351783d64abd3453d681bce63ee9","tid":2027782,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a2b5d6e8953768422ef84e5728e3c3c35ac699e","tid":2027782,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"挽留高質會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"reply